reviewText: When I was a kid my siblings and I would watch the grand canyon video over and over. It's a really great overview of the park with great pictures and history. The other videos were not an interesting.

A really really really nice series, worth watching many times, especially if you can only dream of visiting all of our National Park Treasures. And a great way to revisit the ones you've visited and loved in person. TV the way it should be, in my book.
If You Like To See National Parks and their Beauty and Like Readers Digest, You Will Like This.
